{"tid":801330,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲餐廳用寵物糧煮餸斷正 老闆解釋︰廚師唔識英文","createTime":"2018-08-31T14:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T15:35:57.000Z","uid":150685,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"7707d87b5c040cd1fdb6388e79097aa5a7757a64","tid":801330,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:10:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180830/large/1535637583_12e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180830%2Flarge%2F1535637583_12e8.jpg&h=367dcb84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳洲珀斯的印度餐廳「Cafe Marica」廚師被衞生督察揭發竟然用寵物糧肉類煮餸，周三被罰款。老闆為廚師辯護，指因為廚師不諳英語，故看不懂盒上寫著「寵物肉類」的字眼。<br />\n<br />\n老闆克里斯納斯美（Kopikaran Krishnasamy）說︰「我們一直向有信譽的買手購買羊肉，但最近有客人向廚房推介另一個批發商，於是他們更換了。」<br />\n<br />\n他又解釋，當凍肉送到廚房時，雖然盒上標明「寵物肉類」，但廚師看不懂英文，故一直蒙在鼓裡。「他以為是羊肉，便如常開始準備食物，此時一名食品督察剛來到餐廳。」<br />\n<br />\n老闆強調，那些寵物食糧並未給予客人享用，另外他解釋，供應肉類的經紀在包裝袋上貼上供寵物食用，「只為了避開一些嚴格條例」。不過餐廳最終也被判罰款大約1.4萬澳元（7.98萬港元）兼付堂費。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180831/58626255\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58626255&d=wlg5qpysbMwI8blMwSHqzdU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d0187f9c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180831%2F58626255&h=8addce4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180831/58626255</a>"},{"pid":"281e155d89602ca4ab96f9b0fef6a6c0ebdc88be","tid":801330,"uid":29606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c6f6c500c79456269b16f4d264d8798c81934aed","tid":801330,"uid":77473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:16:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>沒事<span style=\"color: red;\">兒</span>沒事<span style=\"color: red;\">兒</span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"0d7f11cea1b9fe55f2c965afa9c81e8292db3f03","tid":801330,"uid":59030,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:19:33.000Z","msg":"同之前ching chong buger同一區<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d1d009001268773e6bdd2a854c6acb0208bbac","tid":801330,"uid":10707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:26:31.000Z","msg":"食神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1fcba032e0faf63097a5a87965f376acb609965","tid":801330,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:28:02.000Z","msg":"印度佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a74ecdf7f5f19478703773a1b82be103adbb86e0","tid":801330,"uid":108467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:28:19.000Z","msg":"以為用寵物煮餸<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49de37aba1496b41ef055f822f1deced02d4ef85","tid":801330,"uid":156121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T14:33:47.000Z","msg":"D寵物肉同普通肉係超市又真係放埋一堆咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c50ff4f22731cb744736fcbafe9586480f087f7","tid":801330,"uid":25273,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:17:58.000Z","msg":"寵物肉分分鐘貴過普通肉"},{"pid":"40b92124e1435c3dd919a8ad6fc4a60fba53a6a6","tid":801330,"uid":56467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"睇標題仲以為係中國佬做緊"},{"pid":"91ef547919116cc5547a45732ef08dc170d23b23","tid":801330,"uid":47492,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T15:35:57.000Z","msg":"我有批牛肉好平  得閒咪打依個電話囉"}]}